  "text": "The long-term and large-scale use of pesticides leads to environmental pollution and increased pesticide residues in agricultural products, thereby destroying the ecological balance, increasing the risk of food safety, and endangering human health [CITATION_1] . The fluorescent MIPs prepared by molecular imprinting technique is a three-dimensional crosslinked polymer with specific recognition sites, which can realize selective recognition, adsorption, and fluorescence detection of pesticide molecules (template molecules).",
